Package: tinyomics
Title: Explore tiny omics datasets
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: 
    person("Abdullah", "Al-Nahid", , "alnahid@usc.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A lightweight interface to curated omics datasets from various 
    Bioconductor packages. Provides easy access to single-cell RNA-seq, bulk 
    RNA-seq, ATAC-seq, spatial transcriptomics, CyTOF, ChIP-seq, perturbation,
    genotype, and multi-omics datasets. All data returns as tidyomics-compatible
    container classes (SummarizedExperiment, SingleCellExperiment, 
    SpatialExperiment, etc.). Dependencies are loaded dynamically to minimize
    package bloat.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
biocViews: ExperimentData, SequencingData, RNASeqData, SingleCellData
Imports:
    BiocManager,
    utils,
    remotes
